title: Tech takes fifth at Palmetto Intercollegiate - VT hokiesports.com
content: Tech takes fifth at Palmetto Intercollegiate  VT hokiesports.com
description: Virginia Tech's Connor Burgess and Connor Johnson Jr. tied for 17th to lead the Hokies to a fifth-place finish at the Palmetto Intercollegiate, which concluded Tuesday at the par 70, 6,617-yard Palmetto Golf Club.
